    "Transformer-based modelsTable 12 presents the results achieved from the multilingual transformers as well as the Norwegian transformer-based models.ELECTRA base and ELECTRA large show uniform performance across four metrics, each with a precision of 0.69, recall of 0.83, accuracy of 0.83, and a f1-score of 0.75.",
